data.description: Stunning Hood Canal & Mount Rainier views from this immaculately designed 2000 sq ft, 3 bedroom 2 full bath home on 5 acres has engineered vaulted ceilings. The triple wide manufactured home was custom designed to fit this site along with a custom floor plan. The luxurious Pergo floors appear brand new throughout. The gorgeous kitchen goes beyond drawers and cabinets with pantry and built-in glass features. The living room, family room and dining room are well arranged for convenience. Decks  provide spectacular views of the water and mountains. 28x28 detached garage has 15X28 finished rec room and covered deck with hot tub. Outbuildings include 14x16 wired shop.
